docs.text: Publishing ¶ Publishing a new version of the documentation to GitHub pages: $ cd chaoswest-tv.github.io $ mkdocs gh-deploy --config-file ../public-docs/mkdocs.yml --remote-branch master Or use the comfortable way: $ ./tools/publish.sh
